      "retrievedDate": "2026-07-01",
      "quotedText": "Mason Valley Wildlife Management Area: Bass, Crappie, and North ponds, Beaver Slough and that portion of the Walker River within the Mason Valley Wildlife Management Area. Season: Second Saturday in February through September 30. Limits \u2014 Daily: 5 trout and 15 warmwater game fish of which not more than 2 may be black bass. Minimum size for black bass is 14 inches total length. Possession: 10 trout and 30 warmwater game fish of which not more than 4 may be black bass. Hours: Any hour of the day or night."
